 authors) written in English in previous area of research (not necessarily computational biology) with submitted, accepted or published status in journals or conference proceedings</li>\r\n	<li>good spoken and written communication skills</li>\r\n	<li>in addition, applicant must be able to visit Boston for potential interview without visa application</li>\r\n	<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Application Process:</h2>\r\nInterested applicants should submit a letter of interest with a one-page proposal for a project to be conducted in the Liu Lab, CV, and three references (including name and contact information) to xsliu (At) jimmy (Dot) harvard (Dot) edu with subject line “Postdoctoral application”.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', '哈佛大学刘小乐教授课题组', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '102-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-19 09:51:04', '2016-03-19 01:51:04', '', '102', 'http://wpcn.dawneve.cc/2016/03/19/102-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `cn_posts` VALUES ('105', '1', '2016-03-19 16:33:27', '2016-03-19 08:33:27', '这是scripps研究所研究生物信息的，有可能招生：http://sulab.org/research/\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-104\" src=\"http://wpcn.dawneve.cc/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/生物信息学家Andrew-Su（前中）启动了一个众包项目，利用公民科学家在生物医学文献中寻找颠覆性的关联-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"生物信息学家Andrew Su（前中）启动了一个众包项目，利用公民科学家在生物医学文献中寻找颠覆性的关联\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />\r\n\r\n现有项目：https://bitbucket.org/sulab/\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n人员：\r\n\r\n<strong>Andrew Su</strong> is an Associate Professor in the Department of Molecular and Experimental Medicine at the Scripps Research Institute.  Prior to joining Scripps in July 2011, he was the Associate Director of Bioinformatics at the Genomics Institute of the Novartis Research Foundation (GNF) in San Diego, CA. <a href=\"http://sulab.org/author/andrew/\">more…</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Chunlei Wu</strong> is an Associate Professor of Molecular Medicine in the Department of Molecular and Experimental Medicine at the Scripps Research Institute. Prior to joining Scripps in July 2011, he was the Research Investigator II at the Genomics Institute of the Novartis Research Foundation (GNF) in San Diego, CA. <a href=\"http://sulab.org/author/chunlei-wu/\">more…</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n---------------\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'THE sulab', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '94-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-19 16:33:27', '2016-03-19 08:33:27', '', '94', 'http://wpcn.dawneve.cc/2016/03/19/94-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
